function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	local tZombies = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActor(idActorDetector)
	
	if (#tZombies > 0) then
		ShuffleTable(tZombies)
	
		local flTotalGetUpDurationMin = 1
		local flTotalGetUpDurationDelta = 0.5;
		
		local flTotalGetUpDuration = flTotalGetUpDurationMin + flTotalGetUpDurationDelta * Hydra.GetRandomFloat();
		for i, idZombie in ipairs(tZombies) do
			local snoPrimaryPower = Hydra.ActorGetPrimaryPower(idZombie);
			if (Hydra.ActorIsValid(idZombie) and (snoPrimaryPower == 745581 or snoPrimaryPower == 745976)) then
				Hydra.ActorTriggerPhaseJump(idZombie);
				
				Hydra.Wait(flTotalGetUpDuration/#tZombies)
			end
		end
	end
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorDetector) then
		Hydra.ActorDelete(idActorDetector)
	end
end

function spawnMiniBoss(idActorKilled)
	local tBoss = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorKilled, "boss")
	for i, idBoss in pairs(tBoss) do
		Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(MINIBOSS_SUMMON_POWER, "TRANS_IN", idBoss)
	end
end

function spawnSwarms(idActorDetector)
	local proxy = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor("Generic_Proxy", idActorDetector, true, 0, 0)
	Hydra.ActorKill(idActorDetector)
	local idSpawned = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(SNO_SWARM, proxy, false, 0, 0)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idSpawned, P_SUMMONED)
end

function spawnWarriors(idActorDetector)
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorDetector) then
		local proxy = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor("Generic_Proxy", idActorDetector, true, 0, 0)
		Hydra.ActorKill(idActorDetector)
		Hydra.Wait(1)
		local idSpawned = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(SNO_WARRIOR, proxy, false, 0, 0)
		Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idSpawned, P_SUMMONED)
	end
end
